# No API Testing

When testing or verifying features or executing tasks, **never test using the API directly** (e.g., via `curl`, HTTP requests, or API endpoint calls).

You **must** only use the dev panel Web UI (`http://panel.dev.kaiad.dev` or `https://panel.dev.kaiad.dev/`) via the `cursor-ide-browser` tool or manual verification to test and verify changes or to execute application workflows.

Testing via the API bypasses the frontend and does not properly verify that the entire stack (including the UI layer) is working correctly.